HOW TO USE THIS LIBRARY
========================

1. download CustomMarkerImage.jar from http://www.pcnmtutorials.com
2. copy this jar file into /lib folder in your android application project directory.
3. Right click on CustomMarkerImage.jar file and click on Make as Library.

USAGE
========

CustomMarkerImage customImage = CustomMarkerImage.getInstance();
BitmapDescriptor bitmapDescriptor = BitmapDescriptorFactory.fromBitmap(customImage.customMarkerIcon(Color.rgb(7, 166, 30), Color.WHITE, "99"));
mMap.addMarker(new MarkerOptions().position(sydney).title("Marker in Sydney").icon(bitmapDescriptor));

NOTE: mMap means map object of your's google map.
